ry\n\nprint(((n, difference_laundry)))\n```\n```output\n(20, 100.0)\n```\nThe company will have earned $170,000 at the end of \\(\\boxed{20}\\) months. The difference in the amount of laundry Raymond and David do is \\(\\boxed{100}\\) pounds.\n\nWait, let me recheck my solution.\n\n"[0m
